title: Static Analysis

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION.description: Access fine location sources, such as the Global Positioning System on the phone, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine where you are and may consume additional battery power.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

Files may contain hardcoded sensitive in.cwe: CWE-312 - Cleartext Storage of Sensitive Information

MD5 is a weak hash known to have hash co.cwe: CWE-327 - Use of a Broken or Risky Cryptographic Algorithm

SHA-1 is a weak hash known to have hash.cwe: CWE-327 - Use of a Broken or Risky Cryptographic Algorithm

The App uses an insecure Random Number G.cwe: CWE-330 - Use of Insufficiently Random Values

IP Address disclosure.cwe: CWE-200 - Exposure of Sensitive Information to an Unauthorized Actor

App uses SQLite Database and execute raw.cwe: CWE-89 - Improper Neutralization of Special Elements used in an SQL Command ('SQL Injection')

The App logs information. Sensitive info.cwe: CWE-532 - Insertion of Sensitive Information into Log File

"onboarding_diary_message" : "Watching what you eat is so simple! :smile: Tap the plus and add your first food to the diary."
"onboarding_diary_message_first_steps" : "Welcome to YAZIO! We're here to help you take care of the most important tasks for your first day. Take your time and explore all the app has to offer!"

"onboarding_tour_step1_text" : "To reach your goal, YAZIO has calculated your personal calorie goal. But what does that mean for you?

At the top of your diary, you'll find a breakdown of your daily calorie goal. You can see how many calories remain (green) and your daily caloric intake through foods (red). You can improve your calorie balance through activities and sports (yellow).

Your personal calorie goal is based on your current body data (basal metabolic rate - BMR), your average daily activity (physical activity level - PAL) and your goal weight.

At the end of the day, you should try to keep your calorie goal as exact as possible and not to be below or above your goal."

"onboarding_tour_step2_text" : "The central part of a calorie counter is counting your daily calories and nutrients like protein, carbs and fat. This means you should enter everything you eat or drink in your diary.

First, you should track all the foods you've eaten today - whether healthy or unhealthy. For this, click the blue plus button in the diary, search for your foods in our food database or use the camera with the barcode scanner."

"onboarding_tour_step3_text" : "Once you've selected your food, choose a portion size or enter a quantity. Finally, add the product to your diary.

For the first week, you should use a kitchen scale to weigh everything you eat. After a few days, you'll get a good feel for the different quantities.

If you can't find a food item, you can also add new foods to the database or create custom entries in your diary."

"onboarding_tour_step4_text" : "Tracking your daily foods and activities takes a great deal of discipline and patience. That means you'll have to work hard to motivate yourself if you want to reach your goal and create a healthier life for the future.

You should use the first days to customize the YAZIO app. Create favorites for frequently eaten foods, create meals from foods you often eat together or create your favorite recipes.

After that, you can add your favorites, meals, recipes and recently added foods to your diary with the swipe of a finger. Isn't that great?"

"pro_testimonial_larissa_quote" : ""I've actually been unhappy with my figure my entire life. I was often bullied because of it and had tried to lose weight many times before. With YAZIO PRO, I finally got my dream body!""

"pro_testimonial_lena_quote" : ""My husband and I really want children and I just couldn't imagine being an over-weight mom. I want to set a good example for my kids and be able to play and run around with them. Thanks to YAZIO PRO, now I can!""

"pro_testimonial_manuel_quote" : ""Before I started counting calories with YAZIO PRO, I didn't really pay attention to how much I was eating. There was a bratwurst every now and then or sweets and sweetened drinks without end or burgers with fries." "

"pro_testimonial_marc_quote" : ""YAZIO helped me immensely to understand my eating behaviors. From there, losing the weight wasn't such a fight. Once you learn what you have to do, it's unbelievably easy to integrate it into your daily life.""

"pro_testimonial_martina_quote" : ""I don't follow any particular diet. Instead, I count my calories with YAZIO PRO. Although, I do make sure to pay attention to my nutrition and to eat healthy. Now my goal is to get fitter and gain back my self-esteem.""

"pro_testimonial_matthias_quote" : ""I felt uncomfortable in my own skin and hated wearing a swimsuit. I never thought about the choices I was making with my diet. It wasn't until I tried YAZIO PRO that it become particularly easy for me to consciously see what and how much I was eating.""
"pro_testimonial_melanie_quote" : ""So often, my kids would say to me, ‘Mom, you can’t do that. You’re too fat.’ It just wasn’t okay for me anymore. With YAZIO PRO, I finally changed it!""

"pro_testimonial_monique_quote" : ""After looking through some pictures of myself, I saw one that completely shocked me. I've never given much thought to working on myself and never paid attention to what I looked like or how I felt. With YAZIO, that's all changed!""

"pro_testimonial_olivia_quote" : ""I've always struggled with my weight and had tried every diet I could think of. I was never successful. My weight loss was only possible with calorie deficits and YAZIO PRO!""

"pro_testimonial_petra_quote" : ""My legs hurt and I couldn't bare to look at myself in the mirror any more. I had to do something. I downloaded YAZIO and logged my food daily. I was hooked from the beginning!""
"pro_testimonial_rebecca_quote" : ""Don't wait another day. Start now! Every day that you're unhappy with your weight is another day you can't get back. Thanks to YAZIO PRO, I did it!""

"pro_testimonial_sabine_quote" : ""At the time, I was looking for an app to help with self control. Something that I could easily integrate into my everyday routine. That's when I came across YAZIO. For me, YAZIO PRO is exactly what I need, easy and uncomplicated!""

"pro_testimonial_sebastian_quote" : ""In all honesty, I just wanted to do something against the annoying back pain I had. But with YAZIO PRO came the drive to look good and that became my new goal: look good, lose weight, and get fit.""

"pro_testimonial_sissi_quote" : ""I've had problems with my weight since elementary school. A lot of outside influences led to comfort eating, or eating because I was bored or stressed. When I was 11, I went to my first weight-loss camp. I could only ever keep the weight off for short amounts of time. That is, until I found YAZIO!""

"pro_testimonial_sophia_quote" : ""I tried so many times to lose weight, but always for others, never for myself. That's why I always fell short. It wasn't until I started counting calories with YAZIO PRO that it actually worked for me!""

"pro_testimonial_stephanie_quote" : ""Once I saw 290 lb (132 kg) on the scale, it was clear that I couldn't keep living like I was. Once the first few pounds came off, I started to get motivated. From there, I kept setting new goals for myself. With YAZIO PRO, it worked like a charm!""

"pro_testimonial_thomas_quote" : ""When it comes to losing weight, YAZIO PRO is ideal for overview, control and evaluation of your daily diet. I'm convinced that anyone can reach their goal and I hope that my personal success story can motivate others who are just getting started.""

"pro_testimonial_vera_quote" : ""Become conscious of your excuses! I always used thyroid problems (which I actually do have) as an excuse and simply blamed that. Complete nonsense! With YAZIO PRO, you can do it!""

playstore_details.title: YAZIO Calorie Counter, Nutrition Diary & Diet Plan
playstore_details.description:
With the free Calorie Counter app by YAZIO, you can manage your daily food diary, track your activities and lose weight successfully. Counting calories and losing weight has never been so easy!
More than 6 million people have already achieved their New Year’s resolutions with YAZIO. Be a part of it.
YAZIO is the best diet and weight loss app for Android

– Free download and registration
– Personal plan to lose weight or build muscles
– Calorie table with over 2 million foods
– Nutrition tracker and food diary for all meals
– Tracks your calories, carbs, proteins and fats
– Create meals, add favorites or input new foods
– Copy diary entries to other days easily
– Built–in barcode scanner for quick searching
– Tracks your sports, exercises and activities
– Calorie calculator to track your burned calories
– Tracks your daily steps walked and be more active
– Documents your weight with weight tracker
– Assesses your diet and achievements
– Syncs directly with Google Fit
– Use the Wear App to take control
– Great widget and shortcut features

The advantages of YAZIO PRO are undeniable

– PRO is a useful extension of the free app
– With PRO, you will reach your goal twice as fast
– Nutritional plans for low carb, high protein, etc.
– Over 100 healthy and delicious recipes
– Smart and intelligent food rating
– More analysis including diet and body statistics
– Tracks other nutrients like sugar, fiber and salt
– Recognize foods with the most carbs or fat
– Shows progress over the previous 2.5 years
– Tracks body fat, blood pressure and blood sugar
– Measure your breast, waist and hip circumference
– Plan your diet and sports for the next days
– No more advertisements – who doesn’t love that?
– Supports our continuous improvement of YAZIO

You can buy PRO via in–app purchases within the app. YAZIO PRO is significantly cheaper than comparable Calorie Counter apps for diet and weight loss.

If you go PRO, the payment will be charged through your Google Play account during purchase confirmation. The subscription will be auto–renewed shortly before the subscription period ends, maintaining the same price and subscription type you previously purchased, unless you unsubscribe no later than 24 hours before the subscription ends. Subscriptions can be managed through your Google Play account after purchase. It is not possible to refund a subscription or cancel a subscription during the current period.

The storage of your data is extremely safe

The YAZIO Calorie Counter is operated by YAZIO, a German company. Since the app has been developed in Germany, it is subject to the strict German Data Protection Act. All information received or sent through the app is encrypted at all times. All data is stored anonymously on German servers and is not stored by third parties.

– For further assistance go to http://help.yazio.com
– Get to know us better at http://about.yazio.com

Do you want to help make the YAZIO Calorie Counter an even better nutritional & diet app? We always welcome your suggestions and feedback.
